🗝️ 📚
🧩 make_a_pile(n) 👉
   結果 ⬅️ []
   i ⬅️ 0
   🌀 n 👉
      値 ⬅️ 和(n, 積(2, i))
      結果 🧲 値
      i ⬆️
   🔚
   ✅ 結果
🔚
>>> make_a_pile(3) 
[3, 5, 7]
>>> make_a_pile(3) 
[3, 5, 7]
>>> make_a_pile(4) 
[4, 6, 8, 10]
>>> make_a_pile(5) 
[5, 7, 9, 11, 13]
>>> make_a_pile(6) 
[6, 8, 10, 12, 14, 16]
>>> make_a_pile(8) 
[8, 10, 12, 14, 16, 18, 20, 22]